<span data-mce-type="bookmark" style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; overflow: hidden; line-height: 0;" class="mce_SELRES_start">﻿</span> The sale of a business is typically the largest economic event in a business owner’s lifetime. Advance preparation and planning can create significant additional value. Michael Miller and Marcel Goncalves of Merchantec Capital talk about this and the benefits and risks involved when conducting a Sale Readiness Assessment (SRA). Brought to you by Merchantec Capital.